import React from 'react';
import { Container, Nav, NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';


export default function Navbar () {
    return (
        <Container> 
            <Nav>            
                <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link>NOTICIAS</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link>JUDICIALES</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link>DEPORTES</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link>CLASIFICADOS</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link>POLITICA</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>  

                    <NavDropdown>
                        <NavDropdown.Item >Action</NavDropdown.Item> <NavDropdown.Divider />
                        <NavDropdown.Item >Another action</NavDropdown.Item> <NavDropdown.Divider />
                        <NavDropdown.Item >Something else here</NavDropdown.Item> <NavDropdown.Divider />
                        <NavDropdown.Item >Separated link</NavDropdown.Item> <NavDropdown.Divider />
                    </NavDropdown>     
            </Nav>

        </Container>
    )
}
